metadata.name: The Lounge #2 #1/100
metadata.description:
The Lounge for own malts, brandies.  
Open the door and go to a seat you most like, choose the bottle you want whatever it is.  
Pour it into a glass and say 'Hello', 'How are you.' then glass of aged spirit will say you back with 'Quite well'.  
Enjoy every single parts of the whisky, swirl in your mouth and let it go down.  
Absolutely fantastic day will there.
